{"tid":1260602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立即停止推任何有問題嘅帶風向post","createTime":"2019-06-27T01:26:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T02:13:29.000Z","uid":117892,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cf3f1b3edf51dfa8f9abd310c761002eaba90378","tid":1260602,"uid":117892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T01:26:48.000Z","msg":"大家一睇熱門就見到 成堆負皮過千嘅post湧曬上熱門<br />\n唔係話唔好入去鬧佢地 而係應該花時間花精神落去其他更重要嘅post<br />\n灰衫件事 大家都明 集中推一兩個講佢惡行嘅post就夠 因為會有文宣follow up<br />\n<br />\n宜家對我地嚟講 最重要嘅係<br />\n陣間627 10點 天下為公嘅文宣post<br />\n俾啲無聊post蓋過曬 咁點叫人出嚟幫手啊<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以一齊推啲正面、重要、明辯是非嘅post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6bf4a2042e06a51102b71e6d52014686545478d","tid":1260602,"uid":35842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T01:27:10.000Z","msg":"推          <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">大家可以不同意，但記得不譴責！</div></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v91tp44.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv91tp44.png&h=ff06b129&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">拒絕分化、槍口一致<br />\n對準殺人政權<br />\n不退不讓！</div></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">堅守底線，<br />\n因我們沒有退讓的理由。</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZK1hpDrSQ9M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZK1hpDrSQ9M&d=7GYMv7TAV12u%2FDK%2BXNcYJW9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=5ece7113\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZK1hpDrSQ9M</a><br />\n未爭取到五項訴求前，<br />\n香港人將「不撤不散」。<br />\n<br />\n五個訴求包括<br />\n1 &bull; 全面撤回送中惡法&nbsp;<br />\n2 &bull; 反對定性暴動&nbsp;<br />\n3 &bull; 釋放抗爭者 撤銷所有控罪&nbsp;<br />\n4 &bull; 追究濫權警察暴行&nbsp;<br />\n5 &bull; 林鄭下台</div><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/26/232653_dfe28ed01502ee0bc7435027305111eb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F26%2F232653_dfe28ed01502ee0bc7435027305111eb.png&h=8cfbbd31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">不撤不退！</div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">[文宣戰]抗爭告白心聲Poster，</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">請廣傳！！！！</span> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1259733\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1259733</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">可以入post睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最好幫手推埋上熱門<br />\n等多啲人睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">(想share但又懶既直接係最底copy再開！) </span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"a18ef056885ffd5758393db381f8e5e0d1407d48","tid":1260602,"uid":117892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T01:28:16.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbb92b60d58af22e210924c9e3bff2bb286d440a","tid":1260602,"uid":117892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T01:33:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hoTzJdH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhoTzJdH.png&h=efbbd72f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ke3Dqr3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fke3Dqr3.png&h=31a0bebd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6.27 10am 律政中心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bb22eec5012b31d1148886dd55f0341fb218363","tid":1260602,"uid":4931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T01:33:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"